## Relay-T20 MCP End-to-End Test Scenario
**Status:** implemented
**Tags:** stack:backend, module:mcp
**Depends on:** Relay-P6, Chat-P1

Complete validation workflow exercising AutoForge entirely through the MCP interface. Covers project setup, chat sessions, Relay Run execution, gate resolution, handoff submission, and state verification.

### Phase 1: Project Setup

| Step | Tool | Expected Result |
|------|------|----------------|
| 1.1 | `forge_get_project_status` | `{ "project_open": false }` |
| 1.2 | `forge_open_project` | Project metadata with root path |
| 1.3 | `forge_get_project_status` | `{ "project_open": true, ... }` |
| 1.4 | `forge_read_specs` | Specs document with sections |

### Phase 2: Chat Session Lifecycle

| Step | Tool | Expected Result |
|------|------|----------------|
| 2.1 | `forge_create_session` | `{ "id": "fs-<uuid>", "status": "Idle" }` |
| 2.2 | `forge_poll_chat_status` | `{ "status": "Idle", "message_count": 0 }` |
| 2.3 | `forge_send_message` | Assistant reply present |
| 2.4 | `forge_poll_chat_status` | `message_count >= 2` |
| 2.5 | `forge_get_session` (with history) | Messages array with roles |
| 2.6 | `forge_get_session` (without history) | `message_count` present, messages omitted |

### Phase 3: Relay Run Full Lifecycle

| Step | Tool | Expected Result |
|------|------|----------------|
| 3.1 | `forge_list_professions` | Professions array |
| 3.2 | `forge_start_relay_run` | `{ "run_id": "run-<uuid>", "status": "pending" }` |
| 3.3 | `forge_poll_run_phase` | Status "pending" or "running" |
| 3.4 | `forge_poll_run_phase` (poll loop) | Status transitions through steps |
| 3.5 | `forge_get_run` | Complete RunState |
| 3.6 | `forge_list_runs` | Array containing new run |

### Phase 4: Manual Run Control

| Step | Tool | Expected Result |
|------|------|----------------|
| 4.1 | `forge_advance_run` | `ExecuteStep { ... }` |
| 4.2 | `forge_poll_run_phase` | `current_step` incremented |
| 4.3 | `forge_submit_handoff` | Handoff accepted |
| 4.4 | `forge_resolve_gate` (approve) | Gate resolved, run continues |
| 4.5 | `forge_resolve_gate` (reject) | Run routes back to same step |

### Phase 5: Batch Operations

| Step | Tool | Expected Result |
|------|------|----------------|
| 5.1 | `forge_batch_start_runs` | Multiple `run_ids` returned |
| 5.2 | `forge_batch_get_results` | Array of RunBrief objects |

### Phase 6: Spec Workflow Integration

| Step | Tool | Expected Result |
|------|------|----------------|
| 6.1 | `forge_send_message` (spec update) | Message accepted |
| 6.2 | `forge_poll_chat_status` | `pending_changes = true` |
| 6.3 | `forge_approve_spec` | Changes applied |
| 6.4 | `forge_reject_spec` | Changes discarded |
| 6.5 | `forge_read_specs` | Updated specs document |

### Phase 7: File System Operations

| Step | Tool | Expected Result |
|------|------|----------------|
| 7.1 | `forge_browse_directory` | Directory entries |
| 7.2 | `forge_read_file` | File content and metadata |

### Phase 8: Performance & Diagnostics

| Step | Tool | Expected Result |
|------|------|----------------|
| 8.1 | `forge_get_performance_logs` | Recent backend.log lines |
| 8.2 | `forge_list_api_sources` | Configured API sources |
| 8.3 | `forge_test_api_connection` | ConnectionTestResult |

### Phase 9: Cleanup

| Step | Tool | Expected Result |
|------|------|----------------|
| 9.1 | `forge_delete_session` | `{ "deleted": true }` |
| 9.2 | `forge_get_session` | "Session not found" |
| 9.3 | `forge_close_project` | `{ "status": "closed" }` |

